volume history of Japan, to senior councillor {{ill|Matsudaira Sadanobu|ja|松平定信|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * Year 2 of {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|June 30|ja|6月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1869]] ) – Japan's first {{ill|Elementary school|ja|小学校|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} opens in {{ill|Kyoto|ja|京都市|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
