i San'yō|ja|頼山陽|qq=|qq=draft}} presents his {{ill|Nihon Gaishi|ja|日本外史|qq=|qq=draft}} , a 22-volume history of Japan, to senior councillor {{ill|Matsudaira Sadanobu|ja|松平定信|qq=|qq=draft}} . * Year 2 of {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|June 30|ja|6月30日|qq=|qq=draft}} , [[1869]] ) – Japan's first {{ill|Elementary school|ja|小学校|qq=|qq=draft}} opens in {{ill|Kyoto|ja|京都市|qq=|qq=draft}} .
