no|Battle of Nagashino]] takes place. * Year 10 of [[:en:Bunsei|Bunsei]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:June 15|June 15]] , [[1827]] ) – [[:en:Rai San'yō|Rai San'yō]] presents his [[:en:Nihon Gaishi|Nihon Gaishi]] , a 22-volume history of Japan, to senior councillor [[:en:Matsudaira Sadanobu|Matsudaira Sadanobu]] . * Year 2 of [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:June 30|June 30]] , [[1869]] ) – Japan's first [[:en:Primary school|Elementary school]] opens in [[:en:Kyoto|Kyoto]] .
